      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that's a start. but like, when you talk about them \"clashing\" or \"competing,\" is it mostly just these ancient tribal/ethnic rivalries that keep things unstable? it feels like there's a lot of inherent friction between the groups that just can't be solved easily.",
